article_title: Cheyenne Regional Medical Center seeks to sell interest in WINhealth
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms in the afternoon. High 61F. Winds NE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 60%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms in the evening, mainly cloudy late with a few showers. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.author: Becky Orr

og.description: CHEYENNE - Cheyenne Regional Medical Center wants to get out of the insurance business and sell its interest in WINhealth.
